editorialNotes.standard: You donâ€™t need to know a lick of music theory to crank out seriously impressive tunes with Medly. This impressive sequencer lets you create deeply customisable songs with simple gestures: draw a line to add notes, tap to delete, pinch to see the whole track, and more.
